title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-13-2014 MON

The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-13-2014 MON...........PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
The Glenn Beck Program - 1/14/14Monday, January 13, 2014 10:52 AM





Hollywood elite celebrated themselves at the Golden Globe Awards last night,
 but Glenn was mourning a remarkable year old boy who passed away, Sam Berns.

  Also, Marcus Latrell, former Navy Seal and author of Lone Survivor,
   and the movie adaptation that broke box office records over the weekend
     has a heated confrontation with CNN's Jake Tapper regarding the events that occurred
       during operation Red Wings and his brothers' deaths.

  Plus, our pets and why we love them, even when they're bad.
